article.headline: Allen scores 27, Portland State knocks off Northern Arizona 83-68
article.description: — Kaelen Allen's 27 points helped Portland State defeat Northern Arizona 83-68 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Allen scores 27, Portland State knocks off Northern Arizona 83-68
article.story: PORTLAND, Ore. -- — Kaelen Allen's 27 points helped Portland State defeat Northern Arizona 83-68 on Saturday night. Allen also contributed nine rebounds for the Vikings (16-11, 7-7 Big Sky Conference). Kendall Munson and Isaiah Johnson each scored 10 points. The Lumberjacks (12-15, 5-8) were led by Jayden Jackson, who recorded 14 points and four assists. Trenton McLaughlin added 14 points for Northern Arizona. Carson Basham also had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
